{"tid":353452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[2013年4月22日] 四川5年內2強震　三峽大壩肇禍說再現","createTime":"2017-08-09T15:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T02:34:58.000Z","uid":57073,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c55bb75cf2c26ac1b6275692a873f9d3dc6f7c53","tid":353452,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:06:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20130422/195528.htm?t=%E5%9B%9B%E5%B7%9D5%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A72%E5%BC%B7%E9%9C%87%E3%80%80%E4%B8%89%E5%B3%BD%E5%A4%A7%E5%A3%A9%E8%82%87%E7%A6%8D%E8%AA%AA%E5%86%8D%E7%8F%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20130422%2F195528.htm%3Ft%3D%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25B7%259D5%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2585%25A72%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E9%259C%2587%25E3%2580%2580%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25B3%25BD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25A3%25A9%25E8%2582%2587%25E7%25A6%258D%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E5%2586%258D%25E7%258F%25BE&d=DJesqidDmerScbpUKvI81jQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=972200dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20130422/195528.htm?t=%E5%9B%9B%E5%B7%9D5%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A72%E5%BC%B7%E9%9C%87%E3%80%80%E4%B8%89%E5%B3%BD%E5%A4%A7%E5%A3%A9%E8%82%87%E7%A6%8D%E8%AA%AA%E5%86%8D%E7%8F%BE</a><br />\n大陸中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n四川雅安發生強震後，讓長江三峽築壩蓄水對於地質結構的影響，再次被提出來討論。有專家表示，水壩當然會影響位址結構，但不代表這次地震是由三峽工程引起；也有專家認為兩者無關。<br />\n<br />\n雅安市蘆山縣20上午發生芮氏規模7的強震，造成超過180人死亡、1.1萬人受傷。有網友感嘆四川以「天府之國」聞名於世，要是3年、5年就來一次大地震，那就成了「地獄之門」，網友也質疑是不是三峽大壩改變了地質結構。"},{"pid":"ded79c587c2a093083981d9b5a89cfeb459a8d27","tid":353452,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:08:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c93059a3c5c0de11335d7cfa435963612cf83e","tid":353452,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:41:26.000Z","msg":"可信度高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398f3565266127d5c65bc7de33ff9cb7ecf5b1d0","tid":353452,"uid":125382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:44:13.000Z","msg":"多難興邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHing bong hing bong<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b8c38593a2643f49223bcc369c893bd6b1fb51","tid":353452,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T16:27:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d84e75debeb38b0999042804b9a78287779a854","tid":353452,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T02:34:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20130422/195528.htm?t=%E5%9B%9B%E5%B7%9D5%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A72%E5%BC%B7%E9%9C%87%E3%80%80%E4%B8%89%E5%B3%BD%E5%A4%A7%E5%A3%A9%E8%82%87%E7%A6%8D%E8%AA%AA%E5%86%8D%E7%8F%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20130422%2F195528.htm%3Ft%3D%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25B7%259D5%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2585%25A72%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E9%259C%2587%25E3%2580%2580%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25B3%25BD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25A3%25A9%25E8%2582%2587%25E7%25A6%258D%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E5%2586%258D%25E7%258F%25BE&d=DJesqidDmerScbpUKvI81jQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=972200dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20130422/195528.htm?t=%E5%9B%9B%E5%B7%9D5%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A72%E5%BC%B7%E9%9C%87%E3%80%80%E4%B8%89%E5%B3%BD%E5%A4%A7%E5%A3%A9%E8%82%87%E7%A6%8D%E8%AA%AA%E5%86%8D%E7%8F%BE</a><br />\n大陸中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n四川雅安發生強震後，讓長江三峽築壩蓄水對於地質結構的影響，再次被提出來討論。有專家表示，水壩當然會影響位址結構，但不代表這次地震是由三峽工程引起；也有專家認為兩者無關。<br />\n<br />\n雅安市蘆山縣20上午發生芮氏規模7的強震，造成超過180人死亡、1.1萬人受傷。有網友感嘆四川以「天府之國」聞名於世，要是3年、5年就來一次大地震，那就成了「地獄之門」，網友也質疑是不是三峽大壩改變了地質結構。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇完後我覺得起三峽大壩真係好事"}]}